<h2>Energy boosting ideas for vegetables and fruits</h2>
<h3>Fruit</h3>
<ul>
<li>Mix dried fruit with granola for a snack. </li>
<li>Add dried fruit to puddings. </li>
<li>Stir dried fruits into your recipes for baked goods. </li>
<li>Instead of using water, make Jell-O desserts with juice, fruit drinks or the syrup from canned fruits. </li>
</ul>
<h3>Vegetables</h3>
<ul>
<li>Serve raw vegetables with dip. </li>
<li>Serve cooked vegetables with butter and cream sauce. </li>
</ul>
